## 1. Product Vision
Hedge is a secure, operational-first fintech platform for African SMEs and merchants. It handles payment ingestion (MTN MoMo, Telecel, Banks), reconciliation, notifications, and analytics with strong security and auditability.

**Core Promise:** Trustworthy money movement with operational clarity on low-end devices.

